{"data":[{"name":"80:1","price":"ಅವರು (ಪ್ರವಾದಿ) ಮುಖ ಸಿಂಡರಿಸಿದರು ಮತ್ತು ವಿಮುಖರಾದರು.","arabic":"عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5759,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:2","price":"ಒಬ್ಬ ಕುರುಡ ಅವರ ಬಳಿಗೆ ಬಂದರು ಎಂಬ ಕಾರಣದಿಂದ.[1]","arabic":"أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5760,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] ಒಮ್ಮೆ ಪ್ರವಾದಿಯವರು (ಅವರ ಮೇಲೆ ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ ಕೃಪೆ ಮತ್ತು ಶಾಂತಿಯಿರಲಿ) ಕುರೈಷ್ ಮುಖಂಡರಿಗೆ ಧರ್ಮದ ವಿಷಯಗಳನ್ನು ಹೇಳಿಕೊಟ್ಟು ಇಸ್ಲಾಂಗೆ ಆಮಂತ್ರಿಸುತ್ತಿದ್ದಾಗ, ಅವರ ಅನುಯಾಯಿಗಳಲ್ಲಿ ಒಬ್ಬರಾದ ಇಬ್ನ್ ಉಮ್ಮ್ ಮಕ್ತೂಮ್ (ಅಲ್ಲಾಹು ಅವರ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ಸಂಪ್ರೀತನಾಗಲಿ) ಅಲ್ಲಿಗೆ ಬಂದು ಏನೋ ಕೇಳಿದರು. ಅವರು ಕುರುಡರಾಗಿದ್ದರು. ಆದರೆ ಪ್ರವಾದಿಯವರು (ಅವರ ಮೇಲೆ ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ ಕೃಪೆ ಮತ್ತು ಶಾಂತಿಯಿರಲಿ) ಅವರ ಕಡೆಗೆ ಗಮನಹರಿಸದೆ ಕುರೈಷ್ ಮುಖಂಡರಿಗೆ ಆಮಂತ್ರಣ ನೀಡುವುದನ್ನು ಮುಂದುವರಿಸಿದರು. ಇದನ್ನು ಇಲ್ಲಿ ವಿಮರ್ಶಿಸಲಾಗಿದೆ.","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:3","price":"(ಪ್ರವಾದಿಯವರೇ!) ನಿಮಗೇನು ಗೊತ್ತು? ಆ ಕುರುಡರು ಪರಿಶುದ್ಧತೆಯನ್ನು ಪಡೆಯಬಹುದು.","arabic":"وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5761,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:4","price":"ಅಥವಾ ಉಪದೇಶಕ್ಕೆ ಕಿವಿಗೊಟ್ಟು, ಆ ಉಪದೇಶವು ಅವರಿಗೆ ಪ್ರಯೋಜನವಾಗಬಹುದು.","arabic":"أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5762,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:5","price":"ಆದರೆ ಯಾರು ತನ್ನನ್ನು ತಾನೇ ಸ್ವಯಂ-ಪರ್ಯಾಪ್ತನೆಂದು ಪರಿಗಣಿಸುತ್ತಾನೋ,","arabic":"أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5763,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:6","price":"ಅವನ ಕಡೆಗೆ ನೀವು ಪೂರ್ಣ ಗಮನ ಹರಿಸಿದಿರಿ.[1]","arabic":"فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5764,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"[1] ಅಂದರೆ ನೀವು ಕುರೈಷ್ ಮುಖಂಡನ ಕಡೆಗೆ ಪೂರ್ಣ ಗಮನ ಹರಿಸಿದಿರಿ.","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:7","price":"ಅವನು ಪರಿಶುದ್ಧತೆಯನ್ನು ಪಡೆಯದಿದ್ದರೆ ನಿಮಗೇನೂ ದೋಷವಿಲ್ಲ.","arabic":"وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5765,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:8","price":"ಆದರೆ ಯಾರು ನಿಮ್ಮ ಬಳಿಗೆ ಓಡುತ್ತಾ ಬಂದರೋ,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5766,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:9","price":"ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನನ್ನು ಭಯಪಡುವ ಸ್ಥಿತಿಯಲ್ಲಿ,","arabic":"وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5767,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:10","price":"ಅವರ ಬಗ್ಗೆ ನೀವು ಅಸಡ್ಡೆ ತೋರಿದಿರಿ.","arabic":"فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5768,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:11","price":"ಅಲ್ಲ. ನಿಶ್ಚಯವಾಗಿಯೂ ಇದು (ಕುರ್‌ಆನ್) ಒಂದು ಉಪದೇಶವಾಗಿದೆ.","arabic":"كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5769,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:12","price":"ಇಚ್ಛೆಯುಳ್ಳವರು ಅದರಿಂದ ಉಪದೇಶ ಪಡೆಯಲಿ.","arabic":"فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5770,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:13","price":"ಅದು ಪ್ರತಿಷ್ಠಿತ ಗ್ರಂಥದಲ್ಲಿದೆ.","arabic":"فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5771,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:14","price":"ಉನ್ನತವಾದ ಮತ್ತು ಪರಿಶುದ್ಧವಾದ (ಗ್ರಂಥದಲ್ಲಿ).","arabic":"مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5772,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:15","price":"ಅದು ದೇವದೂತರುಗಳ ಕೈಗಳಲ್ಲಿವೆ.","arabic":"بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5773,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:16","price":"ಗಣ್ಯರು ಮತ್ತು ನೀತಿವಂತರಾದ (ದೇವದೂತರುಗಳು).","arabic":"كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5774,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:17","price":"ಮನುಷ್ಯನ ಮೇಲೆ ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ ಶಾಪವಿರಲಿ! ಅವನು ಎಷ್ಟೊಂದು ಕೃತಜ್ಞತೆಯಿಲ್ಲದವನಾಗಿ ಬಿಟ್ಟಿದ್ದಾನೆ!","arabic":"قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5775,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:18","price":"ಅಲ್ಲಾಹು ಅವನನ್ನು ಯಾವ ವಸ್ತುವಿನಿಂದ ಸೃಷ್ಟಿಸಿದನು?","arabic":"مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5776,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:19","price":"ಅವನನ್ನು ವೀರ್ಯದಿಂದ ಸೃಷ್ಟಿಸಿದನು. ನಂತರ ಅವನನ್ನು ನಿರ್ಣಯಿಸಿದನು.","arabic":"مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5777,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:20","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನಿಗೆ ಮಾರ್ಗವನ್ನು ಸುಗಮಗೊಳಿಸಿದನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5778,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:21","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನಿಗೆ ಮರಣವನ್ನು ನೀಡಿ ಸಮಾಧಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ದಫನ ಮಾಡಿಸಿದನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5779,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:22","price":"ನಂತರ ಅವನು ಇಚ್ಛಿಸುವಾಗ ಅವನಿಗೆ ಪುನಃ ಜೀವ ನೀಡಿ ಎಬ್ಬಿಸುವನು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5780,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:23","price":"ಇಲ್ಲವೇ ಇಲ್ಲ. ಅವನು ಇಲ್ಲಿಯ ತನಕ ಅಲ್ಲಾಹನ ಆಜ್ಞೆಗಳನ್ನು ಪಾಲಿಸಲಿಲ್ಲ.","arabic":"كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5781,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:24","price":"ಮನುಷ್ಯನು ತನ್ನ ಆಹಾರವನ್ನು ನೋಡಲಿ.","arabic":"فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5782,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:25","price":"ನಾವು ರಭಸವಾಗಿ ಮಳೆಯನ್ನು ಸುರಿಸಿದೆವು.","arabic":"أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5783,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:26","price":"ನಂತರ ಭೂಮಿಯನ್ನು ಸರಿಯಾದ ರೀತಿಯಲ್ಲಿ ಸೀಳಿದೆವು.","arabic":"ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5784,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:27","price":"ನಂತರ ಅದರಲ್ಲಿ ಧಾನ್ಯವನ್ನು ಬೆಳೆಸಿದೆವು.","arabic":"فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5785,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:28","price":"ದ್ರಾಕ್ಷಿ ಮತ್ತು ತರಕಾರಿಗಳನ್ನು,","arabic":"وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5786,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:29","price":"ಆಲಿವ್ ಮತ್ತು ಖರ್ಜೂರ ಮರಗಳನ್ನು,","arabic":"وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5787,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:30","price":"ದಟ್ಟವಾದ ತೋಟಗಳನ್ನು.","arabic":"وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5788,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:31","price":"ಹಣ್ಣು-ಹಂಪಲುಗಳನ್ನು ಮತ್ತು ಹುಲ್ಲುಗಾವಲುಗಳನ್ನು.","arabic":"وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5789,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:32","price":"ನಿಮ್ಮ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಮ್ಮ ಜಾನುವಾರುಗಳ ಉಪಯೋಗಕ್ಕಾಗಿ.","arabic":"مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5790,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:33","price":"ಕಿವಿಯನ್ನು ಕಿವುಡುಗೊಳಿಸುವ ಆ ಸದ್ದು (ಪುನರುತ್ಥಾನ) ಬಂದಾಗ.","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5791,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:34","price":"ಅಂದು ಮನುಷ್ಯನು ತನ್ನ ಸಹೋದರನಿಂದ ದೂರ ಓಡುವನು.","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5792,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:35","price":"ತನ್ನ ತಂದೆ-ತಾಯಿಗಳಿಂದ.","arabic":"وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5793,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:36","price":"ತನ್ನ ಮಡದಿ-ಮಕ್ಕಳಿಂದ.","arabic":"وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5794,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:37","price":"ಅಂದು ಅವರಲ್ಲಿ ಪ್ರತಿಯೊಬ್ಬ ವ್ಯಕ್ತಿಗೂ ಇತರರ ಕಡೆಗೆ ಗಮನಕೊಡಲಾಗದಷ್ಟು ತನ್ನದೇ ಆದ ಆಲೋಚನೆಗಳಿರುವುವು.","arabic":"لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5795,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:38","price":"ಅಂದು ಬಹಳಷ್ಟು ಮುಖಗಳು ಪ್ರಸನ್ನವಾಗಿರುವುವು.","arabic":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5796,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:39","price":"ಅವು ಕಿಲಕಿಲ ನಗುತ್ತಿರುವುವು ಮತ್ತು ಸಂತೋಷದಿಂದಿರುವುವು.","arabic":"ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5797,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:40","price":"ಅಂದು ಬಹಳಷ್ಟು ಮುಖಗಳಿಗೆ ಧೂಳು ಮೆತ್ತಿಕೊಂಡಿರುವುದು.","arabic":"وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5798,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:41","price":"ಅವುಗಳನ್ನು ಕಾರ್ಗತ್ತಲೆಯು ಕವಿದಿರುವುದು.","arabic":"تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5799,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"},{"name":"80:42","price":"ಅವರೇ ಸತ್ಯನಿಷೇಧಿಗಳು ಮತ್ತು ದುಷ್ಕರ್ಮಿಗಳು.","arabic":"أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ","category":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa"],"ayahNumber":5800,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"kn"}],"chapter":["80 (Abasa)","Abasa","Surah Abasa","Chapter Abasa","Surah 80","Chapter 80","He Frowned","عبس"]}